## Dashboards & Insights

### Dashboard Overview
The dashboards were designed to provide HR leadership with a clear,
high-level view of workforce health while allowing deeper analysis
where required.

### Key Dashboard Views
- Workforce Overview (headcount, tenure, demographics)
- Attrition Trends by department and role
- Performance Distribution across teams
- High-Risk Workforce Segments

### Key Insights
- Certain departments show consistently higher attrition rates
- Early-tenure employees have a higher probability of exit
- Performance distribution highlights potential burnout and support gaps
- Workforce risks can be identified early using combined indicators

### Business Value
These dashboards enable proactive decision-making, targeted interventions,
and continuous monitoring of workforce health.
